{"tid":1491971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人擔心由六月開始到現在，成個政府體系包括各位議員都係演員","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:02:52.000Z","uid":36994,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e1126d427d34bacb53b91a819b2cb464671d94bd","tid":1491971,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:34:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>本人唔係分化撚，我係極深黃巴打。<br />\n但就尋日既斬人案加埋今日驚震全港既醫院變態黑警案，<br />\n警方可以咁快拉到人，其實依兩單野係咪就係自編自導自演，<br />\n我地再回想一下，我地不嬲都係打住【和理非】既旗號去示威遊行。<br />\n【衝擊立法會】、【圍堵中聯辦】、【狗屋放火】、【機場阿伯】等等事件。<br />\n其實會唔會都係一個局？班狗一直都係現場煽動緊在場人士？<br />\n我地連登冷氣軍師不在場，個個都好心水清，因為不分化，不割席，我地無怪前線勇武。<br />\n<br />\n但依一連串既事情都唔係和理非既行為，點解會出現依種畫面？<br />\n我明白係會谷撚氣既，但之前連登日日有人鳩up話火攻、麻包袋等等。<br />\n其實真係等左好耐都無人夠膽做，你可能會話我<br />\n「人地唔做，就話人唔夠薑，依家人地做左，又轉移視線賴到其他野到。」<br />\n其實會唔會係班垃圾局既人一直mon住連登，你地唔敢做，佢地做，之後再屈鳩我地？<br />\n<br />\n我係好擔心，成個政治遊戲都係演員去煽動我地示威者，我唔想我地都係棋子。<br />\n我唔知佢地有咩陰謀論，我亦唔知泛民入面有無鬼！我更加唔知佢地最後目的係乜野？<br />\n但我想大家真係記得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">【我地係無大台】<br />\n同埋我地一直都係向國際表現一個【和理非】既政治活動。</span></span><br />\n<strong><ins>大家萬事要小心，加油！</ins></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"c0de671c71aa3e5beda2fa065a5989be58fd26b7","tid":1491971,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYuV4gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYuV4gf.jpg&h=52b2bc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tri4dee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftri4dee.png&h=7af3e96e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1c30365954a0a89176730f41bb01be1608adc57","tid":1491971,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"曲到圓"},{"pid":"239cfa285326bb1e1056a5cd29922d7acdf8a56c","tid":1491971,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"打左咁多字都無人睇 好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa9a023d82a6208bff132030a46b612e3b7f418","tid":1491971,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"真係諗多左"},{"pid":"0fd6ec5da9c90921d46c643bc7f371967b0facb5","tid":1491971,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"極端中計黨？"},{"pid":"2e5bac0d021cb27fd5383e450b16434d78907cdc","tid":1491971,"uid":261696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"睇得好辛苦"},{"pid":"c83e8ea4679cd66770b051ebdfe61817328333f1","tid":1491971,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"晏就拎左六百個正評 依個post就負多了<br />\n一定係講錯野 迎合唔到大家<br />\nsorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 連登仔係要有證據先信<br />\n所有猜測都係廢話 希望下次可以拎到更多正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7221b10bac51870d1b991ae577288a5e10679535","tid":1491971,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:55:29.000Z","msg":"唔膽心，因為班狗畀人打，心會涼"},{"pid":"12cec2c48ec2b2cf9ae8e6d2985584c14c0a83be","tid":1491971,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"你諗多左啦<br />\n<br />\n而家中共最想你所有野都平熄曬<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁多中計<br />\n<br />\n佢地無咁醒"},{"pid":"739b01f414ef1741821b237e4d93815e20ce25c0","tid":1491971,"uid":130445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"